        <mxCell id="mIkFXSAzH3bALn-NK94c-2" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=16;" value="Lab_mst_01&#xa;Design a WhatsApp system with proper following req:&#xa;1. User Service&#xa;2. Chat Service&#xa;3. Group Service&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;Optimize the chat service for handling the millions of request.&#xa;Specify the type of connection used in the design.&#xa;Determine how the design will be done for LAST SEEN functionality.&#xa;Implement CDC Pipeline int the same architecture." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="270" width="700" x="760" y="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="mIkFXSAzH3bALn-NK94c-3" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=16;" value="&lt;font&gt;Functional Requirements:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;User Service:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;User registration and Login&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;User profile management : create and edit personal details&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;User Settings : time zone, read reciepts, Notifications&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Chat and Group Service:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Ability to create Chat to a particular individual&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Able to create group chat&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Sending and Recieving messages to an individual or in a group chat&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Chat History&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Store and recieve chats&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Group Settings: leave the group, invites , chatting permissions&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Last Seen Funtionality&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Store the date and time of when a message was read by each individual in a dedicated data base&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
